<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= seo ? seo.title : 'Agrim Classes' %></title>
<meta name="description" content="<%= seo ? seo.desc : 'Best Coaching Institute in Deoli' %>">
<meta name="keywords" content="<%= seo ? seo.keywords : 'education, coaching' %>">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css?v=1.1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>

    <script src="header.js"></script>
    <my-header></my-header>

 <section class="breadcrumb-area">

        <div class="shape-globe">
            <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFA500" stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <path d="M2 12h20"></path>
                <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z">
                </path>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="shape-loop">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="#C4C6E5" stroke-width="12"
                stroke-linecap="round">
                <path d="M30,20 Q60,5 80,40 T50,90 T20,60" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="shape-scribbles">
            <svg width="80" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="#FFC07F" stroke-width="3">
                <path d="M80,10 Q90,20 85,30 T90,50" />
                <path d="M60,15 Q70,5 75,25 T80,40" />
                <path d="M90,5 Q100,15 95,25 T100,45" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="banner-content align-left">
                <span class="sub-heading">Agrim Classes</span>
                <h1 class="page-title">IIT-JEE (Mains & Advanced)</h1>
                <ul class="breadcrumb-list">
                    <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="separator"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></li>
                    <li>Courses</li>
                    <li class="separator"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></li>
                    <li class="active">IIT-JEE (Mains & Advanced)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="course-intro-creative">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="intro-grid">
            <div class="intro-main">
                <span class="section-tag">Cultivate Your Dreams</span>
                <h2 class="creative-heading">Cultivate Your Engineering Dreams with <span class="highlight">Agrim Classes</span></h2>
                <p class="creative-desc">
                    Just as fertile soil nurtures seeds to fruition, Agrim Classes cultivates the aspirations of budding engineers. 
                    We prepare you for a promising future in the dynamic world of technology, offering abundant opportunities 
                    to sow the seeds of innovation and progress.
                </p>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-route"></i> Your Pathway to Engineering Excellence</h4>
                    <p>
                        We take pride in being a beacon of guidance and mentorship. Our mission is to empower each student with 
                        the knowledge, skills, and confidence necessary to bloom into accomplished engineers ready to make 
                        a meaningful impact on society.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="intro-features">
                <div class="feature-card-small">
                    <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-drafting-compass"></i></div>
                    <h5>Tailored Coaching Programs</h5>
                    <p>Thoughtfully designed to cater to the diverse needs of aspiring engineers with a focus on holistic development.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card-small">
                    <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i></div>
                    <h5>Transformative Journey</h5>
                    <p>Join Agrim Classes and embark on a journey towards engineering excellence. Let us guide you towards a bountiful harvest of success.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="course-details-section">
    <div class="" style="margin-left: 70px; margin-right: 70px; @media (max-width: 768px){margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px;}">
        
        <div class="course-intro text-center">
            <h2 class="section-title">Crack the Exam with <span class="highlight">Agrim Classes</span></h2>
            <p class="section-desc">
                Our comprehensive classroom program is designed to build a strong foundation for JEE aspirants. 
                We focus on concept clarity, application-based learning, and regular assessment to ensure success.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="boosters-wrapper">
            <h3 class="small-title">Exam Preparation Boosters</h3>
            
            <div class="boosters-grid">
                <div class="booster-card card-red">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-users"></i></div>
                    <h4>India's Best<br>Ever Team</h4>
                </div>

                <div class="booster-card card-green">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-database"></i></div>
                    <h4>Small Batch Size<br>(Special 20)</h4>
                </div>

                <div class="booster-card card-dark-blue">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-book-reader"></i></div>
                    <h4>Doubt Clearing<br>Session</h4>
                </div>

                <div class="booster-card card-light-blue">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="far fa-building"></i></div>
                    <h4>Complete Study Package<br>(Online | Offline)</h4>
                </div>

                <div class="booster-card card-grey">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-download"></i></div>
                    <h4>Fortnight<br>Test</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="eligibility-wrapper">
            <h3 class="small-title">Eligibility Criteria & Details</h3>
            
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="custom-course-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th class="col-criteria">Eligibility criteria</th>
                            <th class="col-details">Details</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="fw-bold">Academic Qualifications</td>
                            <td>Candidates must have passed Class 12</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="fw-bold">Subjects Required</td>
                            <td>
                                <strong>Paper 1 (B.E./B.Tech):</strong> Physics, Mathematics, and any of Chemistry, Biology, or Biotechnology.<br>
                                <strong>Paper 2A (B.Arch):</strong> Physics, Chemistry, and Mathematics.<br>
                                <strong>Paper 2B (B.Planning):</strong> Mathematics is mandatory.
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="fw-bold">Age limit</td>
                            <td>No age restriction for appearing in JEE Main. (Check individual institute criteria for age limits.)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="fw-bold">Minimum Marks in Class 12</td>
                            <td>For NITs, IIITs, and GFTIs: 75% aggregate or top 20 percentile in Class 12. For SC/ST candidates: 65% aggregate.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="fw-bold">Number of Attempts</td>
                            <td>Maximum of three attempts in consecutive years.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="fw-bold">State of Eligibility</td>
                            <td>Determined by the state where the candidate appeared for the Class 12 examination.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="fw-bold">Nationality</td>
                            <td>Indian Nationals, NRIs, PIOs, and OCIs are eligible.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="fw-bold">Important Considerations</td>
                            <td>Candidates from non-recognized boards need an equivalency certificate from the AIU.</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="course-cta text-center">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Enroll Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<my-footer></my-footer>


<script src="footer.js"></script>
</body>
